name: Customized Nike Elite Socks #1
description: This is where you can create your own unique look. Use the menu to select your options. Pricing is as shown. You can view colors here. Please enter color selection in a message upon checkout. You can choose up to three. Each customization starts with authentic Nike Elite socks, and ends where your imagination takes you! Send us a message with special requests or questions. The socks in the photo are dyed with yellow, purple blue, and green. They are not available, but shown as an example of what is possible.

name: Customized Nike Elite Socks #2
description: This is where you can create your own unique look. Use the menu to select your options. Pricing is as shown. You can view colors here. Please enter color selection in a message upon checkout. Please note which color you want on the dominant (longest) stripe. Each customization starts with authentic Nike Elite socks, and ends where your imagination takes you! Send us a message with special requests or questions. Note: The colors used on the sock in the photo are no longer available. It is just to give an example of what is possible. (We have changed the type of dye we use and like the new one much better. New pic coming soon!) The second pic is an example of a two color stripe in ocean blue and china blue. The toe and heel of this sock is not dyed. It was a custom order and is pictured as an example of what is possible.

description: Authentic Nike Elite Socks hand dyed in purple, red, and bright pink. Size M.
